1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:02,583
I used to see, in the solitary cell or the group cell

2
00:00:02,791 --> 00:00:09,750
The names of prisoners, their arrest dates, and reasons

3
00:00:10,916 --> 00:00:15,250
I found the name of a young man I knew from the town of Tabqa

4
00:00:15,541 --> 00:00:20,416
He had written his name and his case on the wall

5
00:00:22,583 --> 00:00:24,791
His name was Muhannad Raja al-Harmoush

6
00:00:25,708 --> 00:00:28,791
They placed him in front of the solitary cell door

7
00:00:29,958 --> 00:00:31,916
Around one o’clock after midnight

8
00:00:33,833 --> 00:00:36,500
I saw them through the window asking his name

9
00:00:36,875 --> 00:00:39,791
He answered, Muhannad Raja al-Harmoush,
so I recognized him immediately

10
00:00:40,041 --> 00:00:43,083
They asked him, What’s your case about?

11
00:00:43,916 --> 00:00:46,041
He said, Mocking ISIS

12
00:00:46,291 --> 00:00:47,750
The interrogator asked, Why do you mock?

13
00:00:47,916 --> 00:00:50,166
He replied, explaining that what he
said was only a joke, nothing more

14
00:00:50,791 --> 00:00:51,916
The interrogator said, No problem with that

15
00:00:52,833 --> 00:00:54,958
Muhannad stayed standing for five minutes

16
00:00:55,208 --> 00:00:56,875
They shackled his hands and blindfolded him

17
00:00:56,958 --> 00:00:58,291
Then took him elsewhere

18
00:00:58,458 --> 00:01:02,541
Through the ventilation opening of the solitary cells

19
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:08,791
Overlooking the car garage

20
00:01:10,041 --> 00:01:11,041
We could hear clearly

21
00:01:11,125 --> 00:01:12,750
They put him in the van

22
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:15,291
Carrying with them tools for digging graves

23
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,291
I concluded they were going to kill and bury him

24
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:21,833
After about two hours

25
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:26,750
The members came back with their tools but without Muhannad

26
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:31,666
They were laughing as if returning from an amusing trip

27
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:34,708
We came to see that as normal

28
00:01:34,875 --> 00:01:37,708
Because it happened regularly from time to time
